OOC:Whoever plays dark One thats a cheap shot from the time I landed and 
attacked I have yet to say one word

::Koj::

Koj sees the the blast closing and gets hit marring his chest plate
knocking him from the tree but manages to keep his focus looking a target. 
Koj gets a targetlock a small panel on his hand opens and fires a small 
round pellet trying shoot it down the tanks cannon barrel.

::Inu-Yasha::

Inu-Yasha seeing his master in trouble growls and opens his mouth as the 4 
cannons inside change around in a circle stoping. As he fires a medium sized 
plasma beam at the Alliance members rushing towards Tavatorn and Dinobot.
